Anticheat Documentation.txt
Minecraft_Cheat_AntiCheat_Findings.md
Reference Analysis & Detection Plan.md
Development Plan.md

# ---- Local reference copy of a prior release (kept local, never committed) ----
oldversion/

# ---- Website (now maintained in the Portfolio repo → https://thoria.fyi/iustitia) ----
# The docs site is generated by scripts/gen_docs.py (from scripts/checks.json) and synced into the
# Portfolio repo's iustitia/ subdir on each release (see CLAUDE.md "Release sync"). The generated
# HTML/CSS/JS is NOT committed to this repo — only the generator (scripts/) + dev docs (docs/*.md,
# docs/superpowers/) live here. These patterns keep a local `gen_docs.py` run from cluttering git.
/index.html
/docs/*.html
/assets/

# ---- Claude Code / commit-message scratch (local only, never committed) ----
.commit-msg.txt
*.tmp

# ---- Internal AI-assistant / dev workflow docs (local only, never committed) ----
# Kept on disk for local dev (Claude Code + superpowers plan/spec workflow) but
# never served on GitHub. The /docs/ subpath pattern matches the entire
# docs/superpowers/ tree (plans + specs).
CLAUDE.md
/docs/TUNING.md
/docs/superpowers/
